    <h1>Activity 1 ‚Äì Rooftop Solar PV System (5 kW)</h1>
    <h3>Block Diagram</h3>
    <pre>
[Roof-mounted 5 kWp PV Array] ‚Üí [MPPT Charge Controller] ‚Üí [Battery Bank]
                                                   ‚Üì
                                            [Hybrid Inverter]
